race.comment: MODELLA (5) brings outstanding form lines to this BM72. Turned in an eye-catcher first-up over 1200m here then chased home Manaal and others in the Racing And Sports Golden Pendant over this course and distance a fortnight ago, beaten just 3.4 lengths. Only needs to hold that form to be winning this. ALABAMA STATE (1) hit the lead and looked the winner only to be claimed late when resuming last time out in a 1300m Midway at this track. Yet to fill a placing in three second-up runs which is a concern, but this looks a nice race for him. DIRECT FIRE (6) raced handy and only tired in the closing stages last time out when second-up. Goes well at this stage of the prep and his 1400m record is sound. Nice chance at odds. VETWELVE (2) beat many of today's rivals home here last start when fresh from a six-week break. Will tighten right up following that run and should be in the finish.  STRAWBERRY IMPACT (12) steps up in grade but has been impressive in two runs at the provincials this prep.
